description:
Boing! Time to simulate a spring force! This challenge fits into chapters 2 and 3 of the Nature of Code and demonstrates how to simulate the oscillating motion of a spring using vectors and forces. https://thecodingtrain.com/CodingChallenges/160-spring-forces.html
